{"tid":1692240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用字要準確 幫助小店就講番係支持","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T05:08:43.000Z","uid":19219,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"012cde3118b6537c8c90e3b7921eccc923c9bb42","tid":1692240,"uid":19219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始連登 FB會懲罰呢個字眼<br />\n去講支持一d 黃絲或者相近理念既店鋪<br />\n首先講到咁係一d 都唔有趣<br />\n文字係有力量<br />\n用錯既文字就會變左出師無名<br />\n加上唔係個個跟每一件事跟到好足<br />\n好多老一輩係停留緊口耳相傳<br />\n或者岩岩學緊用FB<br />\n當佢地聽到大家要去懲罰呢間店鋪<br />\n真係有好多人以為係佢地係藍絲店<br />\n<br />\n麻煩所有文宣改用番d 正面既字眼去支持佢地<br />\n唔好再玩埋d on9 曲線<br />\n名不正 言不順<br />\n唔係個個知網上文宣係直線定曲線"},{"pid":"b9db95419f3bf5ba16916eebe8e09836fdd838cf","tid":1692240,"uid":19219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"用字既重要性可以睇下TVB 既新聞<br />\n用得好就可以改變人睇法"},{"pid":"067f0df1634767dac1360a33574bce0c42d1c06c","tid":1692240,"uid":19219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d466f529b961d5101dc41d1969517291dcd73c9","tid":1692240,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"11月2同11月3之後，整理左少少資訊，得閒可以入黎一齊傾下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"155d908858d3e4f527b49ec6c85df547ceeba069","tid":1692240,"uid":19219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}